<DOCNO> NYT19990309.0058 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-09 10:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3091 &Cx1f; tad-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SHARPDDRIVING-COLUMN1     03-09 0498
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SHARPDDRIVING-COLUMN10-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Ford's takeover of Volvo likely to benefit both
 &HT;    By Linda Sharp
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
