A3187 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A-TEX     03-09 0320
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HOMEOWNERS MAY BE ENTITLED TO MASONITE REFUNDS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By ROGERS CADENHEAD 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Q: What are the details about the lawsuit involving the Masonite
company? I need mine replaced and can't find any information about
it.
</P>
<P>
   _ E.A., Fort Worth
</P>
<P>
   A: Because of three class-action lawsuits settled by Masonite
Corp. last year, homeowners who used some Masonite products may be
entitled to compensation.
</P>
<P>
   The products are Masonite Hardboard Siding, Masonite Woodruf
Roofing and Masonite OmniWood Siding.
</P>
<P>
   Hardboard Siding claims can be filed by calling (800) 330-2722,
and claims for Woodruf Roofing or OmniWood Siding can be filed at
(800) 256-6990.
</P>
<P>
   The company handling the claims has a World Wide Web site at
www.kinsella.com with information about the settlements.
</P>
<P>
   To contact the Masonite Corp., write to Masonite, Building &AMP;
Industrial Products, 1 S. Wacker Drive, Chicago IL 60606.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Is there a Web site address for the current Texas
Legislature? I'm looking specifically for information on House Bill
132.
</P>
<P>
   _ M.H., Arlington, Texas
</P>
<P>
   A: The Texas Legislature Online is at www.capitol.state.tx.us.
</P>
<P>
   You can use the site to read the full text of bills and track
their progress through the Texas House and Senate.
</P>
<P>
   House Bill 132, which would increase the standard retirement
annuity for the state's Teacher Retirement System, was introduced
on Feb. 1 and referred to the House Committee on Pensions and
Investments.
</P>
<P>
   You can also use the site to find out who represents you. Rep.
Ruth Jones McClendon, the author of H.B. 132, can be contacted at
Room E1.510, Capitol Extension, Austin TX 78701.
</P>
<P>
   (Rogers Cadenhead writes a trivia column for the Fort Worth
Star-Telegram. Contact him at trivia(at)prefect.com. Visit the
Star-Telegram's online services on the World Wide Web:
www.star-telegram.com) nn
</P>
</TEXT>
