Dow industrials were up 26, the NASDAQ average up 15. By Kenneth N.
Gilpin.
</P>
<P>
   SONY-REORG (Tokyo) _ In announcing its sweeping reorganization,
Sony is doing nothing less than trying to reinvent itself, changing
from a manufacturer of consumer electronics to a provider of
digital network services similar to Cisco and Lucent. By Stephanie
Strom.
