budget deal to their caucuses in the House and Senate. By Richard
W. Stevenson.
</P>
<P>
   OBIT-GOTTLIEB (Washington) _ Dr. Sidney Gottlieb has died. He
ran the CIA's programs for mind-control, brainwashing, LSD
experiments, germ warfare and assassination by poison in the Cold
War _ and then repented and spent the last years of his life
running leper colonies in India and hospices for AIDS patients in
rural Virginia. By Tim Weiner. (1000 words)
</P>
