Aeronautical Systems vote today on a revised contract proposal from
the company as a strike deadline nears. Some 4,200
Machinists-represented workers began voting before dawn. Results
expected late evening, only a few hours before the scheduled
walkout after midnight. (Thurston, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
