<SLUG> BC-EXPLORATORY10-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    ENDLESS ANNOUNCEMENTS ARE CANDIDATES' BID TO BE NOTICED
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
