<P>
   The industry calls the Daewoo Lanos and other cars in its class
``roller skates,'' meaning they're generally small, sometimes peppy
and almost always low-priced cars targeting first-time buyers and
those looking for basic, no-frills transportation. Give Daewoo
credit, though. The South Korean builder reaches out to some
