   NASCAR
</P>
<P>
   EDs: The Atlanta Journal-Constitution will post a standalone
photo of Jeff Gordon eating breakfast Tuesday with hundreds of kids
at an Atlanta school. No story.
</P>
<P>
   CAR-ATLANTA-TICKETS _ Officials at AMS face slow ticket sales
annually with the March NASCAR race because of an early race date
and unpredictable weather. It's the same situation this year.
That's one reason the event probably will not be televised on
Sunday. (Schlabach, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 10.
</P>
<P>
   CAR-PARK _ Steve Park says he's OK, but there are those who
wonder if the nasty wreck in Atlanta last year took the edge off
his driving and the steam from his promising career. Park, who ran
into the wall during a practice session, was out of racing for
months while recovering from serious injuries. (Schlabach, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
