<P>
   CENTAM-CLINTON _ SAN SALVADOR, El Salvador _ President Clinton
continues his four-day trip to hurricane-devstated areas of Central
America, surveying the rebuilding efforts speaheaded by the U.S.
Army Corps of Engineers and others. Developing. (Lipman, Cox News
