   RJR-NABISCO-BREAKUP (Undated) _ Dismantling what the
swashbuckling corporate mentality of the 1980s had wrought, RJR
Nabisco announces it is breaking up its food and tobacco businesses
and selling its overseas tobacco company to the Japanese,
punctuating the era of mergers, raids and LBOs that it came to
