purchase alcoholic beverages. The legislation, which would confer
more power on state law enforcement officials to crack down on such
activity, also would empower state officials to stop alcohol sales
over the Internet, mail-order catalog or phone in the 20 states
where direct delivery of alcoholic beverages is illegal. By
JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN. (Already filed.)
