Amy Watkins, with hat, poses with two children from her
neighborhood during a Halloween party last year. Watkins, a
26-year-old graduate student from Kansas who had come to New York
to become a social worker, was killed Monday night after she was
stabbed in the back while walking home to her Brooklyn apartment,
police said. (New York Times Photo)
